task.summary:
Removed dedicated "template" dir and working in dist.
Added precompiled bootstrap to repo.
Restructured project. For now without dist directory.
Added bower.json and use OpenLayers via bower.
Switched to leaflet because of better AngularJS support.
Show multiple marker popups, simple test of changing markers

Added global config.
Makes it easy to switch between local dev server and production server.

Makes it easy to switch between local dev server and production server.

Added map events.
Fetch new data when the map is moved or zoomed.

Fixed styling of map.
Don't allow scrolling of the page.
Added name to every post and send lat / long to api.
